==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: fáng rén zhī xīn bù kĕ wú
===Etymology===
Literally: One must not lack a heart that is on guard.
===Proverb===
# You will not survive in life unless are on guard against those would harm you.
